  "text": "Added color variety to the feet in the sprite generator. Now there's a 30% chance that feet will match the body color instead of always matching the node color. This creates more visual variety in the sprite sheet - some agents have unified body+feet looks while others have the contrasting feet that help define their structure. Simple randomization adds a lot of character diversity.",
